  "content": "\n \n \n  <p><br></p>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505123821\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb1hlU5L2xI2tQx2R2wkgFDYkjM35P6V3ZEVSuo42aibsI5MicQGib3ic5NlqOLAdk3ib3psUTNLkCxB1OQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=40b9d8f3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1hlU5L2xI2tQx2R2wkgFDYkjM35P6V3ZEVSuo42aibsI5MicQGib3ic5NlqOLAdk3ib3psUTNLkCxB1OQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;background-color: rgb(127, 127, 127);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;background-color: rgb(127, 127, 127);visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：海狸 好困</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(34, 34, 34);letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;padding: 10px;font-size: 14px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;border-radius: 3px;background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;word-break: break-all !important;word-spacing: 1px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">最近，Ai2</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">耶鲁NYU联合推出了一个科研版「Chatbot Arena」——SciArena。全球23款顶尖大模型火拼真实科研任务，OpenAI o3领跑全场，DeepSeek紧追Gemini挤入前四！不过从结果来看，要猜中科研人的偏好，自动评估系统远未及格。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如今，用AI大模型辅助写论文早已成为科研工作者的家常便饭。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">ZIPDO 2025教育报告显示，AI已经无缝融入70%的研究实验室，并在五年内推动相关科研论文数量增长了150%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mcyakbli125b\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"173\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"600\" data-imgfileid=\"505123835\" data-ratio=\"0.30864197530864196\" width=\"913\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1944\" data-width=\"1944\" height=\"314\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=59c4c6b6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2weL1mbqzpeJk8EHf2ZgslhdNfN4hX1pBYL0G2G0jTI1y8WWJJQicN7LtFckpFaT8kXhoYqlgfQDg%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI在辅助科研的路上一路狂飙，但一个关键问题却长期悬而未解：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">「大模型科研能力究竟怎么样？」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">传统benchmark静态且片面，难以衡量科研任务所需的上下文理解与推理能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为此，Ai2联合耶鲁大学和纽约大学推出了科研界的Chatbot Arena——SciArena，正式开启科学智能的「擂台赛」时代！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mcyait5z8um\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"282\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"876\" data-imgfileid=\"505123836\" data-ratio=\"0.5011441647597255\" width=\"1021\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1748\" data-width=\"1748\" height=\"482\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=321959d6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2weL1mbqzpeJk8EHf2Zgsleo2nMs7WpOLR77RnwrbzYYeBUVlKDPGn9fe7ehwAo01OnqcrSuUBlA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">论文链接：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2507.01001\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2507.01001</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">目前，已有23个最前沿的大语言模型登上SciArena的擂台，涵盖OpenAI、Anthropic、DeepSeek、Google等巨头产品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"718\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1033\" data-imgfileid=\"505123838\" data-ratio=\"1.2784653465346534\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"808\" data-width=\"808\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0cc51120&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1hlU5L2xI2tQx2R2wkgFDYwarXIj7kHWTbHic52qVicRJcicTSthicZD7oGkEZqtkpnQzL7co1K4OEgg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其中，OpenAI o3断崖式领先，坐上了科学任务的头把交椅，在所有科学领域都稳居第一，输出的论文讲解也更有技术含量。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"364\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1215\" data-imgfileid=\"505123837\" data-ratio=\"0.648\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1875\" data-width=\"1875\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9538d260&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1hlU5L2xI2tQx2R2wkgFDYKwjY2sFEibsiaULoRqfqKffEJrcIg2uIQBibSyCH3ibR1zvgYMzMqVv8ibg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其他模型在不同领域各有千秋：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">例如C</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">laude-4-Opus的医疗健康知识很强，而DeepSeek-R1-0528在自然科学表现抢眼</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"496\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1215\" data-imgfileid=\"505123839\" data-ratio=\"0.8823529411764706\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1377\" data-width=\"1377\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1c36b20a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1hlU5L2xI2tQx2R2wkgFDYhCa7v2H9YqNgkSibelP70uYJlW1ZS16cibVk9aW1RdCEWJCa5iaVFgjUQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 1 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">值得一提的是，</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SciArena</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">刚发布没多久</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;p1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">就得到了Nature的特别报道，并被盛赞为「解释大模型知识结构的新窗口</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"264\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"505124893\" data-ratio=\"0.46936542669584247\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1828\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8ce9ec1f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb2weL1mbqzpeJk8EHf2ZgslfTC8tOv4ps4Ta2weLl4mwsruMrZib51h45h4YBHZeOxENPcsmtQl7icA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">下面我们就来看看，评估基础模型科研能力，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SciArena</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">究竟靠谱在哪里？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8bc421a7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 19px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">SciArena：科研AI新「试金石」</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SciArena是首个专为科学文献任务量身定制的大模型「开放式评估平台」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"193\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"566\" data-imgfileid=\"505123841\" data-ratio=\"0.3442822384428224\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1644\" data-width=\"1644\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e158ae80&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1hlU5L2xI2tQx2R2wkgFDY38sicenCXb7KIwSV6Z82fZL6TPVkYduh5BYvJoAIhVRwFoo6ic6DpfxQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在这里，科研人员可以对不同基础模型处理科学文献任务的表现进行比较和投票。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">团队引入了Chatbot Arena式的众包、匿名、双盲对决机制，用真实科研问题来验货大模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SciArena专门针对科学探究的复杂性与开放性进行了优化，解决通用基准测试在科研场景中「失效」的问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">该平台主要由三大核心组件构成：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SciArena平台: 科研人员在此提交问题，并「同台对比」查看不同基础模型的回复，选出自己更偏好的输出。</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">排行榜: 平台采用Elo评分系统对各大模型进行动态排名，从而提供一份实时更新的性能评估报告。</span></span></p></li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SciArena-Eval: 基于SciArena平台收集的人类偏好数据构建的元评估基准集，其核心目标是检验用模型来猜测人类偏好的准确性。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8bc421a7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 19px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">对决背后：评测机制大揭秘</span></strong></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6700c77f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb351381bTy5MO2IN89mV41M88GEiaCCibDxJoaQjYV6HfRtafnmEmfM3R1p0tmkHgBOVuXBD6UJKpsQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">从提问到投票：SciArena评估全流程</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SciArena的工作流程包括检索论文、调用模型回复、用户评估三个环节。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与通用问答相比，科研问答最大的壁垒在于要以严谨的科学文献为依据。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了确保检索信息的质量与相关性，团队改编了Allen Institute for AI的Scholar QA系统，搭建了一套先进的多阶段检索流水线。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"171\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"496\" data-imgfileid=\"505123842\" data-ratio=\"0.30392156862745096\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1632\" data-width=\"1632\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9200cc5f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1hlU5L2xI2tQx2R2wkgFDY6qsNKodtfRk0pdXveI4kia7uzdM0ZSIY1kgJFBhDK4SXAlV4xG5T4qg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">该流水线包含查询分解、段落检索和结果重排序等多个步骤。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">收到用户提交的问题后，平台启用流水线，检索相关的科学论文作为上下文。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">随后，平台把上下文和用户的问题合在一起，同时发送给两个随机选择的基础模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">两个模型各自生成内容详实、附带标准引文的长篇回复。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">平台会统一处理两份回复，变成格式一致的标准化纯文本，以免用户「认出」模型的回答风格。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最后，用户对这两个纯文本输出进行评估，并投票选出自己偏好的答案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"211\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"872\" data-imgfileid=\"505123843\" data-ratio=\"0.3750537634408602\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2325\" data-width=\"2325\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=330eda8d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1hlU5L2xI2tQx2R2wkgFDY0X1iciccAO7RFost9HeVTMEdBAhRVr6s3eic1TnibHl0eDWBrLV6DxDUvA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">值得注意的是，SciArena的注意力主要集中于可横向评估的「通用基础模型」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">至于OpenAI Deep Research等定制型智能体或闭源研究系统，则不在平台的考虑范畴内。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 8px 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505100592\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"292\" style=\"height: 20px;width: 81px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6700c77f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb351381bTy5MO2IN89mV41M88GEiaCCibDxJoaQjYV6HfRtafnmEmfM3R1p0tmkHgBOVuXBD6UJKpsQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">102位专家，13000票</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">要想评测准，数据必须信得过。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">SciArena团队对数据的把关严格得令人发指。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在平台上线的前四个月里，他们收集了不同科研领域的102位专家的13000多次投票。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"243\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"698\" data-imgfileid=\"505123844\" data-ratio=\"0.43246592317224286\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1614\" data-width=\"1614\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3126c89d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1hlU5L2xI2tQx2R2wkgFDY3AfUJLs5Ub7fRM9LZFj8xRT9d87MibZnr087fvdVk1yNncFVxGibybWg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这102位专家绝非随意参与的路人，而是科研一线的在读研究生，人均手握两篇以上论文。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而且，所有的标注员都接受了一小时的线上培训，确保评价标准一致。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">再加上盲评盲选机制，SciArena的每一条评估结果都有据可依。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在SciArena的高标准和严要求下，平台的标注数据自我一致性极高（加权科恩系数κ=0.91），标注者间一致性也达到了较高水平（κ=0.76）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mcsw3ux0q0z\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"431\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"566\" data-imgfileid=\"505123840\" data-ratio=\"0.7669376693766937\" style=\"width: 57%;flex-basis: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"738\" data-width=\"738\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7f98baad&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1hlU5L2xI2tQx2R2wkgFDYUbrrEPEwaAVu3zib9y5Pgfgm9MYQiahx7X1eYrIb862fhY0iaJXJzsF0w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这13000多次投票为SciArena平台打下了值得信赖的评估基础。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8bc421a7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 19px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">最强AI，猜不透科研人的心</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在SciArena平台上，研究团队基于元评估基本集SciArena-Eval，测试了「模型评模型」的自动评估方法：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">给一个评估模型一条科研问题和两个模型的回答，让它猜哪个更可能被人类选中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">结果很扎心。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">哪怕是表现最好的o3模型，准确率也只有</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">65.1%</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，而像Gemini-2.5-Flash和LLaMA-4系列，几乎跟「掷硬币选答案」的准确率差不多。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mcsw42mq1rri\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"762\" data-backw=\"560\" data-height=\"762\" data-imgfileid=\"505123846\" data-ratio=\"1.3607142857142858\" style=\"width: 57%;flex-basis: auto;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"560\" data-width=\"560\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=68ba3921&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1hlU5L2xI2tQx2R2wkgFDYhMeQNsbQiaHp401nicujRFRRpAllia96w0LmmcGIbvyqQoiceKgAeZe46A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对比一下通用领域，像AlpacaEval、WildChat这些基准的评估模型，准确率都能跑到70%以上，相比之下，科研任务显得难多了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">看来，「让模型理解科研人的偏好」并非易事。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不过也不是全无亮点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">加入了推理能力的模型，在判断答案优劣上普遍表现更好。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">例如，o4-mini比GPT-4.1高出 2.9%，DeepSeek-R1也小胜自家模型DeepSeek-V3。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这说明，会推理的AI更懂科研问题的本质。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究团队表示，SciArena-Eval未来有望成为科研AI评估的「新标准」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它能帮我们看清AI到底有没有真正「读懂」科研人的心思。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://allenai.org/blog/sciarena\" target=\"_blank\">https://allenai.org/blog/sciarena</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2507.01001\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2507.01001</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;min-height: 1em;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://the-decoder.com/sciarena-lets-scientists-compare-llms-on-real-research-questions/\" target=\"_blank\">https://the-decoder.com/sciarena-lets-scientists-compare-llms-on-real-research-questions/</a></span></span></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "SciArena 作为全球首个科研 LLM 竞技场，评估 23 款顶尖模型在真实科研任务中的表现，OpenAI o3 领跑，并揭示了自动评估在科研场景的局限。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "SciArena 作为全球首个科研 LLM 竞技场，评估 23 款顶尖模型在真实科研任务中的表现，OpenAI o3 领跑，并揭示了自动评估在科研场景的局限。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了由 Ai2、耶鲁大学和纽约大学联合推出的全球首个科研大模型竞技场 SciArena。该平台旨在解决传统基准测试在评估大模型科研能力方面的局限性，通过众包、匿名、双盲对决机制，让科研人员对 23 款顶尖 LLM 处理科学文献任务的表现进行真实比较和投票。文章公布了首批评测结果，显示 OpenAI 的 o3 模型在所有科学领域均断崖式领先，DeepSeek 和 Gemini 也表现突出。SciArena 引入了先进的多阶段检索流水线以确保科学文献的质量与相关性，并基于科研专家的 13000 多次投票构建了可信赖的评估基础。然而，研究发现，即使是表现最好的模型（如 o3），其自动评估科研任务的准确率也仅为 65.1%，远低于通用领域，表明让 AI 理解科研人偏好仍面临挑战。SciArena 被《自然》杂志报道，被誉为“解释大模型知识结构的新窗口”。",
